**Why:** A sibling root cause surfaced under the SAME diagnostic signature
("pre-commit fails on a file I never touched; empty `git diff` vs origin/main").
The blocker this time was a `ruff check` lint violation, not `ruff format`
drift. KEY DIFFERENCE: `ruff check --fix` did NOT auto-resolve `SIM102` (the
nested `if` under an `elif` chain is a manual/unsafe fix), so re-running the
formatter cannot clear it ‚Äî you must hand-edit (combine the nested `if` into
the `elif` with `and`). The fix shape matched the original skill: land a
